Package: tidyTRY
Title: Read, Clean, and Process Plant Trait Data from the TRY Database
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Billur", "Bektas", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "billur.bektas@example.com")
Description: Provides a pipeline for processing plant trait data downloaded
    from the TRY database (<https://www.try-db.org/>). Handles reading large
    tab-delimited TRY data files with chunked processing, filtering by species
    lists, resolving taxonomy via TNRS or WorldFlora, removing experimental
    datasets, cleaning quantitative traits by error risk, renaming long TRY
    trait names to short codes, extracting geolocation data, and generating
    diagnostic summaries and plots.
